import classNames from "classnames/bind";

import styles from "./CreateAccount.module.scss";
import Input from "../../../components/Input";
import Button from  "../../../components/Button";

const cx =classNames.bind(styles);

function Account() {
    return ( 
        <section className={cx("Container")}>
            <article className={cx("itemLeft")}>
                <Input 
                    name="Name"
                    type="text"
                    required
                    title="Can not be empty"
                    id="Name"
                />
                <Input 
                    name="Email"
                    type="email"
                    required
                    title="Can not be empty"
                    id="Email"
                />
                <Input 
                    name="Images"
                    type="file"
                    required
                    title="Can not be empty"
                    id="Images"
                    multiple
                />
                <Input 
                    name="Birthday"
                    type="date"
                    required
                    title="Can not be empty"
                    id="Birthday"
                />
                <Input 
                    name="From"
                    type="text"
                    required
                    title="Can not be empty"
                    id="From"
                />
                <Input 
                    name="Password"
                    type="password"
                    required
                    title="Can not be empty"
                    id="Password"
                />
                <Input 
                    name="Majors"
                    type="text"
                    required
                    title="Can not be empty"
                    id="Majors"
                />
                <Input 
                    name="Maxim"
                    type="text"
                    required
                    title="Can not be empty"
                    id="Maxim"
                />
                <Input 
                    name="Describe"
                    type="text"
                    required
                    title="Can not be empty"
                    id="Describe"
                />
                <Input 
                    name="CV"
                    type="file"
                    required
                    title="Can not be empty"
                    id="CV"
                />

            </article>
            <article className={cx("itemRight")}>
                <article className={cx("job")}>
                    <Input 
                        name="Job"
                        type="text"
                        required
                        title="Can not be empty"
                        id="Job"
                    />
                    <Button
                        name="Your Job"
                        w
                    />
                </article>
            </article>
        </section>
     );
}

export default Account;
